069900
070000
070100     MOVE    "N"                     TO      CH-NOTFOUND.
070200
070300     FIND    GERCHASSISE             AT
070400             GER-CHASSI              =       IN-CHASSI
070500       ON    EXCEPTION
070600        IF   DMSTATUS (NOTFOUND)
070700             MOVE  "S"               TO      CH-NOTFOUND
