072200******************************************************************
072300*                    LEITURA NOVAPLACDS    P/ CHASSI             *
072400******************************************************************
072500
072600 070-E-NOVAPLACHA.
072700
072800
072900
073000     MOVE    "N"                     TO      CH-NOTPLAC.
073100
073200     FIND    NOVAPLACSE2             AT
073300             NPL-CHASSI              =       IN-CHASSI
073400       ON    EXCEPTION
073500        IF   DMSTATUS (NOTFOUND)
073600             MOVE    "S"             TO      CH-NOTPLAC
073700             GO                      TO      070-S-NOVAPLACHA
073800        ELSE
073900             DISPLAY "PC/GEV/T441/DB: FIND ERROR NOVAPLACSE2"
074000             PERFORM 140-E-ERRODB    THRU    140-S-ERRODB
074100             CALL    SYSTEM          DMTERMINATE.
074200
074300***  PLACA ATRIBUIDA PARA O CHASSI.... VERIFICAR NO DETRAN
074400     IF      NPL-SITUACAO            >       5
074500             MOVE  009               TO      IA1
074600             GO                      TO      070-S-NOVAPLACHA.
074700
074800***  PLACA EM PROCESSO DE ESCOLHA, NAO ALTERAR
074900     IF      NPL-SITUACAO            =       4 OR 5
075000             GO                      TO      070-S-NOVAPLACHA.
075100
075200
075300 070-S-NOVAPLACHA.
075400     EXIT.
075500
